text.div:
This case-sensitive code system http://hl7.org/fhir/us/mcode/CodeSystem/snomed-requested-cs defines the following codes:

CodeDisplay
USCRS-34947 Surveillance Epidemiology and End Results Program Extent of Disease, 2018 edition (tumor staging)
USCRS-34949 Enneking surgical staging system (tumor staging)
USCRS-34955 UICC Classification of Malignant Tumours 8th Edition (tumor staging)
USCRS-34956 UICC Classification of Malignant Tumours 7th Edition (tumor staging)

name: SnomedRequestedCS
title: Requested SNOMED Codes Code System
description: Codes requested from SNOMED by mCODE, to be issued at a later date. Where numeric codes are given, these correspond to the expected SNOMED CT codes. Terms beginning with 'USCRS-' (for United States Content Request Service) represent request identifiers with no SNOMED code yet approved or assigned.
